title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 14 2021

description:
Joe Biden divided us over covid, and now he hectors Americans to stop being divisive. Testy Terry McAuliffe sees VA slipping away. Chappelle and Netflix standing firm on freedom of speech. Squid Game: As Buck gets older, he's a bit queasier on some forms of game violence. NBA player out for season due to covid vax side-effects.
